pr_title: pdftoraster filter converted to filter function
pr_body: I will look into changing the extension of `filter/pdftoraster.cxx` to `filter/pdftoraster.c`. Changing it initiates `make` issues so currently it is in the form of `.cxx`. Will resolve soon.

pr_title: Rastertopwg filter converted to filter function.
pr_review_comments: [{'comment_id': 663548234, 'comment_body': 'Do not use `getenv()` in a filter function, instead, read the variable in the CUPS filter stub (`filter/rastertopwg.c`) and transfer the requested output format as a parameter. See the `ghostscript()` and `pdftopdf()` filter functions and the CUPS filter stubs `gstoraster` and `pdftopdf`. You can also use the type `filter_out_format_t` for the parameter here.', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2021, 7, 4, 19, 43, 46, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'tillkamppeter', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 663549952, 'comment_body': 'The PPD you get via the filter data (`data->ppd`) here you also do not need to use `getenv()` and also should not use it.', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2021, 7, 4, 20, 2, 7, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'tillkamppeter', 'type': 'User'}]
